oria's  consort,  Prince Albert of Saxe-Coburg-Gotha ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Albero von Matsch was born in 1242, his father, Hartwig II von Matsch, was 28 and his mother, Sophia Gräfin von Moosburg, was 27. He married Sophia von Feldthurns genannt von Stain in 1263, in Austria. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died on 10 January 1280, in Austria, at the age of 38."},"et":{"1242–10 January 1280":"1242–10. jaanuar 1280","1242–1280":"1242–1280","1244–1301":"1244–1301","1245–Female":"1245–Surnud","1273–1328":"1273–1328","1214–1249":"1214–1249","1216–Female":"1216–Surnud","1242":"1242","20 December 1249":"20. detsember 1249","1263":"1263","10 January 1280":"10. jaanuar 1280","1273":"1273","1280":"1280","1216":"1216","1249":"1249","1214":"1214","1301":"1301","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","1328":"1328","Österreich":"Austria","Lienz, Tirol, Österreich":"Lienz, Tirol, Austria"},"fi":{"1242–10 January 1280":"1242–10. tammikuuta 1280","1242–1280":"1242–1280","1244–1301":"1244–1301","1245–Female":"1245–Kuollut","1273–1328":"1273–1328","1214–1249":"1214–1249","1216–Female":"1216–Kuollut","1242":"1242","20 December 1249":"20. joulukuuta 1249","1263":"1263","10 January 1280":"10. tammikuuta 1280","1273":"1273","1280":"1280","1216":"1216","1249":"1249","1214":"1214","1301":"1301","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","1328":"1328","Österreich":"Itävalta","Lienz, Tirol, Österreich":"Lienz, Tirol, Itävalta"},"fr":{"1242–10 January 1280":"1242–10 janvier 1280","1242–1280":"1242–1280","1244–1301":"1244–1301","1245–Female":"1245–Décédée","1273–1328":"1273–1328","1214–1249":"1214–1249","1216–Female":"1216–Décédée","1242":"1242","20 December 1249":"20 décembre 1249","1263":"1263","10 January 1280":"10 janvier 1280","1273":"1273","1280":"1280","1216":"1216","1249":"1249","1214":"1214","1301":"1301","1245":"1245","1244":"1244","1328":"1328","Österreich":"Autriche","Lienz, Tirol, Österreich":"Lienz, Tirol, Autriche","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Albero von Matsch est né en 1242, son 